        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Distribute: $2x(3x^2 - 2x - 4) + 5(3x^2 - 2x - 4) = 6x^3 - 4x^2 - 8x + 15x^2 - 10x - 20$. Combine like terms: $6x^3 + 11x^2 - 18x - 20$."
